Name: AdGroupId
Notes: The ID of the AdGroup.

Name: AdGroupName
Notes: The name of the AdGroup.

Name: AverageCpc
Notes: The total cost of all clicks divided by the total number of clicks received.

Name: AverageCpm
Notes: Average Cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM).

Name: BenchmarkAverageMaxCpc
Notes: Indicates how other advertisers are bidding on similar products. Not compatible with the field Device on the Product Partition Report.

Name: BenchmarkCtr
Notes: Indicates how other advertisersâ€™ Product Listing Ads for similar products are performing based on how often people who see their ad end up clicking on it. Not compatible with the field Device on the Product Partition Report.

Name: CampaignId
Notes: The ID of the Campaign.

Name: CampaignName
Notes: The name of the Campaign.

Name: ClickConversionRate
Notes: The number of converted clicks divided by your total clicks that can be tracked to a conversion. This is how often a click on your ad resulted in a conversion. Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: ClickType
Enum Values:
URL_CLICKS / Headline
CALLS / Phone calls
OTHER / Other
PRODUCT_EXTENSION_CLICKS / Product plusbox offer
SITELINKS / Sitelink
PRODUCT_LISTING_AD_CLICKS / Product listing ad
GET_DIRECTIONS / Driving direction
OFFER_PRINTS / Print offer
BREADCRUMBS / Breadcrumbs
CALL_TRACKING / Manually dialed phone calls
MOBILE_CALL_TRACKING / Mobile phone calls
LOCATION_EXPANSION / Get location details
UNKNOWN / unknown
Notes: The Impressions field will reflect how often the ad was served with that click type available. Since ads can serve with multiple click types displayed, impressions may be double counted and the totals may not be accurate.

Name: Clicks
Notes: The number of clicks.

Name: ConversionRateManyPerClick
Notes: The number of conversions divided by total clicks that can be tracked to conversions. Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: ConversionValue
Notes: The sum of conversion values for all conversions.

Name: ConversionsManyPerClick
Notes: This column reports total conversions, across all the conversion actions you're tracking. How you've chosen to count your conversions (unique or all) affects the number shown in this column.

Name: ConvertedClicks
Notes: The number of clicks that converted within your chosen conversion window.

Name: Cost
Notes: The sum of your cost-per-click (CPC) and cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM) costs during this period. Other costs such as cost-per-call aren't included. For a sum of all costs, use the TotalCost column.

Name: CostPerConversionManyPerClick
Notes: Total cost divided by your total conversions.

Name: CostPerConvertedClick
Notes: Cost divided by your total converted clicks.

Name: CpcBid
Notes: Cost per click bid. Values can be one of: a) a money amount in micros, b) "auto: x" or "auto" if AdWords is automatically setting the bid via the chosen bidding strategy, or c) "--" if no CPC bid applies to the row.

Name: CriteriaDestinationUrl
Notes: Destination URL of the criterion that triggered ads. In the Destination URL report, this field behaves as a segment.

Name: Ctr
Notes: The number of clicks your ad receives (Clicks) divided by the number of times your ad is shown (Impressions). Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: Date
Notes: The date formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: DayOfWeek
Enum Values:
MONDAY / Monday
TUESDAY / Tuesday
WEDNESDAY / Wednesday
THURSDAY / Thursday
FRIDAY / Friday
SATURDAY / Saturday
SUNDAY / Sunday
Notes: The name of the day of the week, e.g., "Monday".

Name: Device
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / Other
DESKTOP / Computers
HIGH_END_MOBILE / Mobile devices with full browsers
TABLET / Tablets with full browsers
Notes: Device type where the impression was shown.

Name: FinalAppUrls
Notes: List of final app URLs of the main object of this row.

Name: FinalMobileUrls
Notes: List of final mobile URLs of the main object of this row.

Name: FinalUrls
Notes: List of final URLs of the main object of this row.

Name: Id
Notes: ID of the main object of this row.

Name: Impressions
Notes: Count of how often your ad has appeared on a search results page or website on the Google Network.

Name: IsNegative
Notes: Indicates if the criterion for this row is a negative (exclusion) criterion.

Name: Month
Notes: The first day of the month, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: MonthOfYear
Enum Values:
JANUARY / January
FEBRUARY / February
MARCH / March
APRIL / April
MAY / May
JUNE / June
JULY / July
AUGUST / August
SEPTEMBER / September
OCTOBER / October
NOVEMBER / November
DECEMBER / December
Notes: The name of the month of the year, e.g., "December".

Name: ParentCriterionId
Notes: Criterion ID of the product partition's parent.

Name: PartitionType
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / Unknown
SUBDIVISION / Subdivision
UNIT / Unit
Notes: The partition type of the ProductPartition criterion.

Name: ProductGroup
Notes: Path to the ProductPartition, including all of its parent partitions.

Name: Quarter
Notes: The first day of the quarter, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd. Uses the calendar year for quarters, e.g., the second quarter of 2014 starts on 2014-04-01.

Name: SearchImpressionShare
Notes: The impressions you've received on the Search Network divided by the estimated number of impressions you were eligible to receive. A percentage returned as "xx.xx%", or the special values "< 10%" or "> 90%". Not compatible with the field ClickType on any report. Not compatible with the field Device on the Product Partition Report.

Name: TrackingUrlTemplate
Notes: Tracking template of the main object of this row.

Name: UrlCustomParameters
Notes: Custom URL parameters of the main object of this row.

Name: ValuePerConversionManyPerClick
Notes: The total value of all conversions divided by the total number of conversions.

Name: ValuePerConvertedClick
Notes: The total value of all conversions divided by the total number of converted clicks.

Name: Week
Notes: The date for the Monday of the week, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: Year
Notes: The year, formatted as yyyy.
